title.rendered: What Devices is Dumpster Compatible With?

content.rendered:
Dumpster works on all Android-based devices from Android 4.1 (Jelly Bean) and above. 
With Dumpster Cloud, all of your Dumpster files will be saved to your account. Meaning you can access them on any Android device as long as you are logged into your account.
